#

Spiced Pear Salad

15 min
$10
220 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

NutsDairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Salad

Tags:

SaladLightFresh

Description

A refreshing salad featuring sweet, spiced pears paired with crunchy walnuts and a light dressing.

Ingredients

  • mixed greens: 4 cups
  • ripe pears: 2, sliced
  • walnuts: 1/2 cup, toasted
  • feta cheese: 1/3 cup, crumbled
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • balsamic vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • honey: 1 teaspoon
  • cinnamon: 1/4 teaspoon
  • black pepper: to taste
